KERNAL COMPILATION  AND BANNER CHANGING IN KERNAL:
==================================================

DOWNLOAD THE LINUX A5d2x source from git or clone the git
 Enable the toolchain
      . /opt/pOKY-tiny/2.5.2/environment
 cd init
 vi version.c
    cont chat arry we have to chnage the banner
 cd ..
  make distclean
  make ruggudboard _a5d2x defconfig
  make
  cd arch/arm/boot
  cp zimage /var/lib/tftpboot
  cd dts
  cp rba5d2x-rugged.dtb /var/lib/tftpboot
  
  
  sudo minicom -s
  
  setenv serverip 192.168.1.1
  setenv ipaddr 192.168.1.33
  ping 192.168.1.33
  
  copy the zimage and oftree images commands  //It will find in Ruggedboard.community.com
    sf probe
    tftp
    sf write
    sf erase
  saveenv
  reset
  
